{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_12_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――仕事後の帰り道",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、お疲れ様\n今日の収録、大盛り上がりだったな",
      "startTime": 3.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.5666667025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あぁ、ありがとうございます\nでも普段通りにしただけですよ",
      "startTime": 10.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.1666667025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……そうだ、スタッフさんから手土産にって\n話題のプリンシェイクをもらったんだ。飲んでみるか？",
      "startTime": 19.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、そうなんですね……後で飲んでみますね",
      "startTime": 22.5666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.7666673382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はなんか変だぞ。いつものこころなら\nプリンって聞いただけで真っ先に飛びつくじゃないか",
      "startTime": 31.4000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "というか最近ずっとそうだ。この間橋本さんが事務所に\nプリンを買ってきた時も、リアクションが薄かったし",
      "startTime": 39.3490800876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.1333340049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとなんですかそれー。様子がおかしいかどうかの\n判断基準がプリンなのはおかしくないですかー！？",
      "startTime": 46.9528729061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.8333322247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "プリンを愛するこころだって\nたまにはプリンと距離を置きたい時だってあります！",
      "startTime": 52.7333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.3333322247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "さては最近こころに構ってもらえなくて寂しいんですね\nこころ不足ならそう言えばいいのに～",
      "startTime": 61.5333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.2333322247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "物足りないっていう意味ではそうかもしれないな\nとはいえ、仕事では特に変わったことはないし……",
      "startTime": 69.1666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、学校で何かあったのか？\nまぁ、無理には聞かないが……",
      "startTime": 76.9333321889,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5889.3056839000055,
          "startTime": 82.8226378728
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.4333322247
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.8226378728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "大したことじゃないですから、別に心配いりま――\nあれ、雨？　わー！　どんどん強くなってます！",
      "startTime": 83.2261978947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.983333242
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.983333242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "雨宿りはナイス判断ですが、ちょっと遅かったですね～\n制服びしょびしょ……明日は学校ないからいいですけど",
      "startTime": 95.2999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2999999087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "でもどうやって帰りましょうかねー\nこんな中を濡れて帰ったら絶対風邪引いちゃいますよ",
      "startTime": 104.5333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今、タクシーをアプリで探しているんだが……\nすまん、どうも近くにいないようだ",
      "startTime": 112.1297147498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.433333242
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　どれだけついてないんですかぁ\nお……見て下さい、あのお店の前！　あれ可愛いです！",
      "startTime": 120.5333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　おお、めずらしい傘が並んでるな\nあの傘、やけにピカピカしているが……",
      "startTime": 129.8999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4999999087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "知らないんですか～？　オーロラ傘っていうんですよ\nSNS映えしますし、小物としても優秀なんです",
      "startTime": 137.8333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.933333242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　ご褒美にプレゼントしてくれるんですか！？\nしょうがないですね～、受け取ってあげましょう",
      "startTime": 145.7039747425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "何も言っていないのに、勝手に話を進めないでくれ\nでも、そうだな。雨もやみそうにないし、特別だぞ？",
      "startTime": 153.8333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.5666665753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "本当にいいんですか？　やったー！\n冗談のつもりでしたけど、言ってみるもんですね～",
      "startTime": 162.9860265963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.9666665753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "あ、レインコートも着て雨コーデってのもアリですね\nあそこに売ってますよ！",
      "startTime": 170.9666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "傘だけでも特別に買ってあげるんだから\nこれで我慢してくれ",
      "startTime": 175.5128948887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.333333242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　せっかくこころの好感度を上げる\nプレゼントチャンスだったのに、いいんですか～？",
      "startTime": 180.6999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.4999999087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "なーんて、ふふ、本当にありがとうございます！\nおかげで雨の日の楽しみが出来ちゃいました！",
      "startTime": 189.0333332062,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7206.666793799996,
          "startTime": 196.24
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（最近浮かない顔が多かったから、元気になって良かった）\n（ん？　仕事の連絡か。ああ、この案件なら……）",
      "startTime": 197.4836218786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 204.2666675926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.2666675568
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.2666675568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr016.m4a",
